metadata.description: Prepare for World War D! We thought the dinosaurs were all gone. We were dead wrong! 65 million years ago, a species of evolved dinosaurs left our Earth, and now they're back! It's the Jurassic War of the Worlds as these Neosaurs commence a massive invasion to reclaim their planet and make mankind extinct!
metadata.name: Dinowars Jurassic War of the Worlds
